description: The abandonment of plans to develop the Ramsey building is "disappointing", a commissioner says.
title: Charity's decision over Ramsey Courthouse plans 'a blow'
title_page: Charity's decision over Ramsey Courthouse plans 'a blow' - BBC News
maintext: "It is a great disappointment that the team have not been able to secure all the funding they anticipated to progress... although in the current climate, it is less surprising," he said.
